fields.value: Replication Data for: "ARE COMPETITIVE BANKING SYSTEMS REALLY MORE STABLE?"

dsDescriptionValue.value: This site provides all the Stata data and do files necessary to reproduce the results in the paper, "ARE COMPETITIVE BANKING SYSTEMS REALLY MORE STABLE?", jointly authored with Samangi Bandaranayake and Kuntal Das.
